    static class IeeeConversionTesterClasses.AssignIEEELongsTester
extends TesterClasses.Conversion_T2Q_Tester<long[]>
    A tester class to test Quadruple.assignIeee754(long[]).
    Obtains the test data from IeeeConversionTesterClasses.q2ieeeConversionDataList() and performs Quadruple.assignIeee754(long[]) as the tested operation.
